pull_request.title: Item ratings
pull_request.body:
Adds item ratings to be used in the [clientside PR](https://github.com/smogon/pokemon-showdown-client/pull/2171). They should be accepted at the same time. The following ratings were also changed:
- Auspicious Armor, Malicious Armor, Masterpiece Teacup, and Unremarkable Teacup are now Useless items, for obvious reasons.
- Big Nugget is now a Usually useless item; the old algorithm said items there are for Fling only, which it is.
